headline: A Fresh Look at CMS Energy’s Valuation After Regulatory Wins and Leadership Changes
summary: CMS Energy (CMS) has seen a string of activity lately, including new leadership appointments and ambitious plans for upgrading its natural gas pipelines. In addition, recent regulatory decisions are adding confidence about the company’s growth trajectory. See our latest analysis for CMS Energy. Momentum around CMS Energy is building, as the company’s regulatory wins and executive moves have coincided with a year-to-date share price return of 8.8% and a 1-year total shareholder return of 4.7%...
